                  <b> Efficient Tensor Decomposition. </b> [<a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2007.15589">ArXiv</a>|<a href="https://www.cambridge.org/core/books/beyond-the-worstcase-analysis-of-algorithms/8A8128BBF7FC2857471E9CA52E69AC21"> Book Link </a>| <a href="javascript:toggle('abstract36')"> Abstract</a>]
